      "research_type": "review",
      "paper_scope": "This paper reviews the effects of silicon (0.59-1.56 wt.%) and phosphorus (0.001-0.07 wt.%) on κ-carbide precipitation, tensile properties, Charpy V-notch impact toughness and dynamic fracture toughness of Fe-30Mn-9Al-0.9C base lightweight austenitic steels, as well as their application potential in transportation and military fields."
